{"html":"<h2>Tactic(s)</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: Counter_Monotonicity<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: C<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;=&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;&lt;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;last\\(&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;DCtrIs\\(d,C&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;DCtr&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: IV_Uniqueness<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: C<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;=&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;&lt;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\"> | </span>regex&quot;last\\(&quot;<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;IV\\(&quot;<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">tactic</span>: Key_IntegrityAndConfidentiality<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">presort</span>: C<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">prio</span>: {id}<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;regex&quot;CreateKey\\(ek,&quot;</p><br/>\n","title":"Tactics"}